reviews.text: Went twice, avocado toast & poached eggs was great! Egg & toast the second time was just that - egg and dry toast. Egg was perfectly poached though. Great iced latte.

Always a reliable place for your coffee in this area of Sheung Wan. There's a lot of competition around it, but they always deliver a good coffee.

Quite a few brunch and lunch plates in offer, but I tend to prefer their coffee over their food.
Amazing Latte! Amazing French Toast! I feel so sorry for myself that I never know French Toast can be so delicious🤔(not a fan of any kind of toast) You should definitely try it!

Another cafe hunting! It is my second time to cupping room. The food quality is good as usual, I think it is actually quite difficult for a cafe or a restaurant to maintain the quality of food but Cupping Room did it. 

Ordered a quiona bowl with greens and poached egg. It was tasty especially the quiona, it mixed with some dried raisin and red beans.

The only one thing I will complain is the portion. It is quite expensive for a small portion.
Nice cozy joint. Great Western-style breakfast spot! The food and coffee were delicious. Definitely a recommendation

reviews.text: 美好的一日😉
好鐘意這的意粉啊，保持好水準，好食！Flat White 有香濃咖啡味☕🍽

늦은 아침. 아침식사는 거르고 모닝커피가 땡겨 근처에 맛있는 커피점이 있나 찾아봤는데 블로그에서 보고 찾아 갔습니다. 라떼를 좋아해서 저는 라떼. 아들은 아이스 커피와 토스트를 주문. 커피맛은 신맛이 매우 강한 원두를 사용하는것 같습니다. 지금까지 먹어본 커피중 가장 신맛이 강하네요. 라떼는 제가 무거운 맛의 라떼를 좋아하는데 역시 진하고 무거운...대신에 신맛이 나는 라떼였습니다. 맛은 매우 좋았습니다. 그런데 함께 주문한 토스트는 아주 오래 걸려 나오네요. 빵을 약간 굽고 반숙계란 얹어서 나오는건데 꽤걸리네요... 암튼 홍콩와서 맛있는 커피먹고 갑니다.
Went twice, avocado toast & poached eggs was great! Egg & toast the second time was just that - egg and dry toast. Egg was perfectly poached though. Great iced latte.

Always a reliable place for your coffee in this area of Sheung Wan. There's a lot of competition around it, but they always deliver a good coffee.

Quite a few brunch and lunch plates in offer, but I tend to prefer their coffee over their food.
